I dont think you need to take the test. Just follow these steps
First round your current age to the nearest 10
Next find how many people of yoir age you can take on
Then divide your age so that the quotient is 5
Then multiply the divisor by 5
Then multiply that by however many people of your age you can take on
Bam you got your answer
Example im 16 so i round it to 20
Then lets say i can take on 3 20 year olds
Now i divide 20 by 4 so my quotient is 5
Then i muliply 5 by 4 then that by 3 
So i can take on 60 5 year olds or a number close to that.
This method is for a general answer to how many you can take on so dont think over think it.
Most of the time the answer has to be minimized a bit
